claim.claim-text:
A method of providing application feedback comprising:
detecting selection of an option to send a recommendation for an application;
enabling selection of at least one contact;
incorporating application feedback related to a group associated with at least one selected contact; and
sending the recommendation and the application feedback to the at least one selected contact.

9. The method of any one of claims 1 to 8, further comprising:
detecting selection of an option (154) to send a recommendation for an application;
enabling selection of at least one contact (158);
incorporating application feedback related (70) to a group (20) associated with at least one selected contact (158); and
sending the recommendation and the application feedback (70) to the at least one selected contact (158).
